title: Player Attack S03E13 HDTV h264-Berg
description:
We're at Oz Comic-Con in Adelaide this week, catching up with some of their esteemed guests!

Watch Jessica melt while talking to Neil Kaplan, the voice actor who's appeared in what feels like everything from Digimon to Bleach to Transformers: Robots in Disguise and - of course - StarCraft II (yes, he's the voice of Tychus Findlay!).

Find out what's been going on in the world of actor/director/all-round clever clogs storyteller Michael Hurst since he hung up the sandals and bowed out as Iolaus from Hercules: The Legendary Journeys.

...and then there's a couple of fellas, Daniel Portman and Finn Jones, who you might recognise from a little show called Game of Thrones.

Plus, of course, we have all the latest gaming news - this is Player Attack!
